In the MATTER OF Gregg D. TRAUTMANN, an Attorney at Law (Attorney No. 015061993) D-89 September Term 2017
080765 Supreme Court of New Jersey. February 16, 2018

ORDER

This matter having been duly presented, it is ORDERED that GREGG D. TRAUTMANN of DENVILLE , who was admitted to the bar of this State in 1993, and who was suspended from the practice of law for a period of six months, effective August 14, 2017, by Order of this Court filed July 13, 2017, be restored to the practice of law, effective immediately.
